    <item>
      <title>刺激政策持续乐观推动中国股市延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者继续押注北京方面最新的刺激措施将有助于推动市场好转并提振中国低迷的经济，中国股市周三延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口商担忧导致泰铢升至 2022 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国刺激计划提振了全球风险资产，泰铢升至 30 个月来的最高水平，这给泰国央行带来了采取行动抑制泰铢升值的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:27:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据支持进一步降息，金价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-high-as-us-data-supports-deeper-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国数据疲软，进一步降息的可能性增强，黄金价格继上一交易日上涨逾 1% 后，再创历史新高。白银价格接近四个月来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-high-as-us-data-supports-deeper-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币兑美元汇率自 2023 年 5 月以来首次突破 7</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/yuan-rallies-past-7-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者消化了一系列支持中国经济的措施，且美联储近期降息导致美元处于弱势，人民币兑美元汇率 16 个月来首次突破 7 大关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/yuan-rallies-past-7-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:09:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
